headline: Delta Says It Has Started 2026 "Great Momentum" -- Time to Buy the Stock?
summary: The airline continues to defy the overall industry, with management noting in its latest quarterly update that it's already off to a great start in 2026.

headline: MarketBeat Week in Review – 01/12 - 01/16
summary: Economic data helped stocks move higher as it showed that the Fed's decision on interest rates may not interrupt the bullish case for equities in 2026.

headline: How a Rate Cap Would Shrink Credit-Card Rewards
summary: President Trump’s proposed 10% cap on interest rates would force issuers to be more selective with their reward programs. That would hit users with lower credit scores.
